This topic falls under the sub-category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). The paper also involves the use of algorithms and machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be classified under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
